profile:
We are a proffesional Design and Build Landscape Contractor.  We service the Western Toronto, From Etobicoke to Hamilton and beyond.  We take pride in the work we do, and spend time with each an every potential client to ensure the final outcome meets their expectations.  We are not your discount Landscaper, we are meticulous, and set high standards for ourselves.  

We offer Landscape Design, Contruction, and Lighting.  We take on jobs from as small as walkways to as large as complete backyard makeovers.  We have Finished carpenters on staff, so consider us your one stop shop for all your outdoor needs, from decks to interlock patio's, flagstone, to complete outdoor (12v) lighting systems.  

We look forward to hearing from you.  

Lou'ay & Mark

profile:
Welcome to Easy Pools

Does looking out at your underwhelming backyard fill you with ideas of the extraordinary space it could be?
A beautiful setting to entertain friends, a private oasis for relaxation and rejuvenation, a place the kids never tire of! You want to make the most of your property – and your free time – but when it comes to pool designs and pool landscaping, maybe you’re not sure where to begin. We encourage you to make the most of your time by taking an hour of ours. Start with just an hour talking with us to get an idea of the real possibilities for your space. Customizing your whole pool experience is something we’re passionate about!

About Us:

IT’S A MATTER OF TIME.
We’re all so short on time today. We need to make the most of the downtime we have with unforgettably great experiences.
At Easy Pools we understand that, and we know that having a beautiful backyard space with a fabulous pool is one of the best ways to create those great times – right outside your own door.
We’ve found that we can help you achieve that ideal space by giving fully of our time, from planning to completion, to ensure you end up with a pool setting that will add real value to your home, and your home life.

That means you can feel free to ask as many questions as you want, whenever you want – we’ll have all the time you need. It also means that during the construction phase we take our time to deliver superb workmanship. No cutting corners. No details left undone. Ensuring your needs are met by spending our own time wisely is how we work. It’s what makes us different.

For over ten years, Easy Pools  has been creating beautiful properties for homeowners in the GTA, including landscapes, stonework, patios, outdoor structures and pools. 

Over the years, we’ve perfected our project management skills so that your projects are not only finished on time and on budget, but client courtesy is core. There is always a dedicated manager to stay in touch with you, promptly answering calls or meeting to discuss the project. Staff always operate in a safe, conscientious and friendly manner.

We appreciate you taking the time to find out about us and we hope you find what you need. If you’d like to discuss the possibility of adding a pool to your home, we would love to hear from you.

Our Services Include:
*Swimming Pool Features: vanishing edges, expanding underwater steps, baja steps for lounging, customzied chapes, naturalized surroundings, integrated waterfalls and waterspouts, integrated or freestanding spa pools
*Beautfiul Utility Features: In-pool and surrounding lighting, safety fencing, utility sheds / cabana / shower or bar area, slope-adjusting retaining walls
*Landscaping
*Lighting

profile:
Bancheri Bros Interlocking & Paving Ltd. is an landscape design company specializing in interlocking paver installation, pool installation and asphalt paving.  

With over 20 years of experience in interlocking and paving installations, we will help you create a distinctive design element that will enhance your homes appeal, increase its value and offer a unique look that only Bancheri Bros. can offer. Bancheri Bros. is a family owned and operated business. We take pride in all our work and offer written guarantees as well as a lifetime guaranty on the structural integrity offered by the manufacturer. All of our employees are experienced and well trained in installing and working together to provide a superior amount of quality, workmanship and costumer satisfaction.

Bancheri Bros. Interlocking and Paving Corp. has installed countless driveways, walkways, retaining walls, steps and patios of all shapes and sizes. Each job is customized and designed to suit each and every single site, we offer free on-site consultations and estimates for every job.

Why Choose Bancheri Bros. as your interlocking installer?

Bancheri Bros. Interlocking and Paving Corp is a family owned and operated busines, this means that at all times there is an owner supervising the site. This helps ensure sure the quality and workmanship of all our projects are beyond the customers expectations.

For over 20 years Bancheri Bros. has always been about customers first. We have all of the latest tools and equipment to accommodate any size job, we can offer products from any of the top industry suppliers and we start and finish each job on time and efficiently.
products: Interlocking concrete pavers are a smart and elegant design choice. They are manufactured to withstand weight and weather. They are laid in bedding sand just as flagstone, cobblestone, and brick, but they interlock to provide a perfect, stable fit. They come in a wide variety of colors, shapes, textures, and designs. Interlocking pavers are easy to maintain and they provide an excellent drainage system for your driveway.

ELP Landscapes is a woman-led company spearheaded by Cheryl Cichon. 
In every project, she brings extensive experience in the construction industry and an innovative industry-leading approach to professional project management.

Professionalism:
A high degree of professionalism is imbued in every aspect of our work and is a central pillar of who we are and how our staff conduct themselves on-site. 
Ask us about our new GPS-equipped trucks and why it makes a difference in ELP projects.

Building Relationships:
We pride ourselves on being transparent and putting an emphasis on communication.

Project Management:
From the design phase, to when the space is ready for you to enjoy , we put project management first. 
Doing things the ELP way means that regardless of project scale, we hold ourselves accountable and aim to be on time, on budget, and on track.

Quality We Stand By:
Premium and long-lasting materials, industry veterans and quality workmanship, and an unrivalled management process. 
ELP-finished projects are held at the highest standard of quality and sophistication.

profile:
We are an award-winning luxury pool company that specializes in designing and building your custom outdoor oasis.

We are a full service pool company with 47 years of experience in transforming back yards. 
We’ll install, repair or renovate any type of pool. Concrete, vinyl, fiberglass and steel pools. 
We offer a wide range of services to both builders and homeowners. From design and build projects to delivery of pool chemicals and weekly service.

Our experience gives us a competitive advantage.

Unparalleled quality, unmatched price and the best customer service in the business.

profile:
Award Winning Swimming Pool Service Company and Retail Store. Specializing in liner replacement, safety covers, equipment replacement and water chemistry. Total Tech Pools was started in 1991 primarily as a pool service company. Many of the original staff came from other pool companies and many are still with us today. Total Tech Pools performs all types of repairs, restorations, and maintenance on pools including liner replacement, openings/closings, equipment installation and repair, leak detection and complete new pool installations.

In 1996 a retail store was opened and in 2001 a larger facility was opened in Oakville. Currently Total Tech Pools operates a store in Oakville , ON, Kingston, ON and Montreal, QC. We offer a full line of chemicals, equipment, accessories and many other supplies for your pool at very affordable prices. Total Tech Pools prides itself on providing honest and fair service and places a very strong emphasis on education and training.

We are very proud to have received the Small Business of the Year Award in 2009. We truly appreciate the support from our customers, staff, suppliers and other partners for helping us earn this prestigious award.

AWARD WINNING SERVICE TEAM
Our award winning Service Team has been serving customers for 20 years. At Total Tech, we pride ourselves on fair, knowledgeable, and honest service at terrific prices. To experience our service is to understand what sets us apart from the rest. We encourage you to book your experience today.

products:
We carry a full line of pool and spa products with quality and value in mind. All our products have been carefully researched in order to provide the best products available at optimum prices. Total Tech Pools and Spas is located at 1380 Speers Rd in Oakville.

We carry a full line of pool related products:

    Liquid Chlorine (Sodium Hypochlorite)
    Pool and Spa Chemicals
    Accessories and Maintenance Products
    Pool Toys and Games
    Have a very well stocked Parts Department
    Various Equipment (pumps, filters, heaters, sanitation systems, automation)
We have a fully functional and landscaped pool at our Renovation Showroom next door which will help you visualize liners, landscaping options, lighting options and equipment.
Outdoor Furniture
services:
Total Tech Pool & Spa offer most, if not all, pool/spa related services ranging from professional openings & closings, pool liner replacements & restorations, leak detection & repair, equipment installation & repair, to weekly pool maintenance service.
POOL INSPECTION:
    A visit to the home by one of our expertly trained staff members
    A full written report which details the current condition of the pool surface, equipment and foundation.
    The report will outline anything that is not functional or up to code and provide the approximate cost to fix/ replace these dysfunctional parts.
    The report will give any additional recommendations such as safety hazards in the backyard and pool accessories (ie. winter covers, diving boards, slides, fencing, etc).

POOL MAINTENANCE
    Chemical balancing
    Water testing
    Vacuuming
    Leaf Skimming
    Equipment Maintenance

POOL REPAIRS
Our technicians are trained and experienced in a variety of pool related repairs and are backed up with vast technical resources and an extensive parts department. We will identify the problem and advise you on corrective measures and if applicable how to prevent recurrence.
POOL RENOVATIONS/ BACKYARD LANDSCAPING
Total Tech, either independently or in conjunction with our landscaping firm, Rosa and Rosa, can completely transform your backyard and pool.
POOL LEAK DETECTION
We utilize a variety of methods to locate leaks including pressure testing, sonar detection, and diving. In most cases we can isolate a leak to a very small area.
POOL EQUIPMENT INSTALLATION
POOL LINER REPLACEMENT
Total Tech Pools and Leisure is your complete pool service provider.

profile:
Premier Pool Group provides full swimming pool, spa and fountain service and repair to help keep your residential or commercial system running smoothly. We recommend meeting you on-site for a no-charge, no-obligation analysis of your swimming pool equipment. We dispatch one of our full-time, year-round employees to complete the service. We offer single or multiple days per week service to match your needs. Call us for ongoing service, start-ups, one-time cleanings, pool inspections or whatever your pool needs might be. We service, renovate & install  in ground pools. above ground pools, on ground pools, water falls and spa's. We are family owned and operated, licensed, and insured. Our employee's are Certified Pool Operators. We maintain our database and training yearly and follow The City of Toronto Public Health Department recommendations to ensure compliance for your health and safety.
